                "date_valid": ["2002"],
                "description": ["Technology Education in Oklahoma is an instructional program that provides young men and women (Grades 6-10) with daily, hands-on exploratory experiences and insights into technology and career opportunities so that they can make meaningful occupational and educational choices."],
