                "date_modified": ["1415392140"],
                "date_valid": ["2010"],
                "description": ["The State Board of Education recommended and approved the Indiana Academic Standards for Dance in May 2004 under the Indiana General Assembly's direction to develop standards that are \"world-class, clear, concise, jargon-free, and by grade-level.\" The Indiana Academic Standards for Dance incorporate the National Standards for Arts Education, which were developed by the Consortium of National Arts Education Associations."],
                "identifier": ["http:\/\/asn.jesandco.org\/resources\/D10002FE", "http:\/\/purl.org\/ASN\/resources\/D10002FE"],
