                "date_modified": ["1426600786"],
                "date_valid": ["2009"],
                "description": ["The Iowa Core Curriculum for Science reflects the belief that ALL students should experience science through a curriculum that is rigorous, relevant, global in its perspective, collaborative in nature, and connected by strong visible links to other areas of study. This document follows the format and content of NSES in which there are eight categories of standards."],
