                "date_valid": ["2013"],
                "description": ["This framework document provides an overview of the standards that are grouped together to form the units of study for Algebra II. The standards within each unit are grouped by conceptual category and are in the same order as they appear in the Common Core State Standards for Mathematics. This document is not intended to convey the exact order in which the standards within a unit will be taught nor the length of time to devote to the study of the unit."],
                "identifier": ["http:\/\/asn.desire2learn.com\/resources\/D2605466"],
