                "date_valid": ["2010"],
                "description": ["Revised in 2010, this essential guide for curriculum developers\u2014department chairs, superintendents, teachers, education professors\u2014was designed to teach our nation's schoolchildren about basic economics and the economy. Helping young people develop economic ways of thinking and problem solving prepares them to be wise consumers, investors, and savers."],
