                "description": ["This course is designed to provide 7th and 8th grade students with an introduction and comprehensive overview of the fields of information and communication, construction, manufacturing, energy, power, and transportation technologies. Students will also develop an understanding of the history of technology and how the design loop is used to solve technological problems."],
