                "date_valid": ["2015"],
                "description": ["The redesigned Core French curriculum presents what students are expected to know, do, and understand in Grades 5 through 12. It provides a framework through which teachers can engage students in learning experiences that offer opportunities to become proficient users of French, gain new perspectives, and participate in Francophone communities."],
